Enstratius,provides,a,suite,of,tools,to,help,enterprises,manage,their,cloud,infrastructure,It,supports,the,provisioning,management,and,automation,of,applications,in,all,leading,public,and,private,clouds,Enstratius,is,available,as,either,software,as,a,service,or,on,premises,software,Enstratius,RESTful,API,enables,customers,to,make,authenticated,calls,against,Enstratius,from,existing,applications,or,third,party,tools